data.description:
** Motivated Seller** 
** 5K TOWRDS CARPET CHANGE ALLOWANCE OR CLOSING COST OFFERED**
Located in the popular Trolley Run Subdivision. This Energy Efficient Green SMART HOME can be controlled right from your smart phone, voice command or from the Smart device. Control the lights, outlets, blinds, doors, AC, Bedtime modes, Morning modes and so much more! 
This Green Smart Home built in 2016, has 4 BEDS 2.5 Baths, a tankless water heater, spacious bedrooms, a large open kitchen and family room, and hardwood flooring and granite countertops throughout. 

Vancouver Station in Trolley Run Subdivision: US 1 HWY 118 Bypass Intersection, turn towards USC Aiken, Trolley Run Subdivision will be 1.2 miles ahead. Turn into Trolley Run Blvd. At first round about veer right.
Also verify the school information on your own.
